msgid "An explosive device. When it explodes, it will hurt living beings and destroy blocks around it. TNT has an explosion power of @1. With a small chance, blocks may drop as an item (as if being mined) rather than being destroyed. TNT can be ignited by tools, explosions, fire, lava and redstone signals."
msgstr ""

msgid "An explosive device. When it explodes, it will hurt living beings. TNT has an explosion power of @1. TNT can be ignited by tools, explosions, fire, lava and redstone signals."
msgstr ""

msgid "TNT"
msgstr "三硝基甲苯（炸药）"

msgid "Ignited by tools, explosions, fire, lava, redstone power"
msgstr "可由工具、爆炸、火焰、岩浆、红石能量来引燃"

msgid "Explosion power: @1"
msgstr "爆炸强度：@1"

msgid "Place the TNT and ignite it with one of the methods above. Quickly get in safe distance. The TNT will start to be affected by gravity and explodes in 4 seconds."
msgstr "放置好三硝基甲苯，然后用上述方法之一将其引燃。迅速撤离到安全距离之外。三硝基"
"甲苯将开始受重力影响，并在4秒后爆炸。"
